#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/tips.lua:4 input:4 standard
msgid ""
"Don’t forget that druids are working only when there are trees nearby. All "
"buildings occupied by druids need trees in their surroundings."
msgstr ""

#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/tips.lua:8 input:8 standard
msgid ""
"The traffic on Gallic roads is heavy. Keep in mind that you will need to "
"spare some big green building spaces for warehouses."
msgstr ""

#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/tips.lua:12 input:12 standard
msgid ""
"Ensure that you can produce all building materials before you start growing "
"your economy."
msgstr ""

#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/tips.lua:16 input:16 standard
msgid ""
"Reed yards need open waters to grow reed. If you don’t see any right at the "
"beginning of a new game, make finding it your priority."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Log, part 1
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:92 input:92 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid ""
"Log is an important basic building material. It is also used for charcoal "
"production."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Log, part 2
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:94 input:94 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid ""
"Logs are produced by felling trees. Woodcutters need forester’s houses "
"nearby to take care of the supply of trees."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Granite, part 1
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:105 input:105 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid ""
"Granite is a basic building material. You also need it for production of "
"bricks."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Granite, part 2
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:107 input:107 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid ""
"It is mainly produced by stonecutters, but iron mines and tin mines also "
"produce some. Especially basic tin mine can help you, when there is not "
"enough rocks in your surroundings. This mine is also the only one that "
"produces primarily granite while empty."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Planks, part 1
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:118 input:118 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid "Planks are an important building material."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Planks, part 2
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:120 input:120 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid "They are produced out of logs by the sawmill."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Planks, part 3
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:122 input:122 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid "They are also used by the weapon smithy."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Clay
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:133 input:133 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid "Clay is made out of water and mud to be turned into bricks."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Sanded Wood
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:144 input:144 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid ""
"Bricks are an important building material. They are made out of a mix of "
"clay and granite dried in a coal fire."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Reed
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:154 input:154 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid ""
"Reed is grown on shores of lakes and rivers by reed yards. Nothing is better "
"suited to make roofs waterproof. It is also used to make baskets and fishing "
"nets."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Wool
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:165 input:165 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid "Wool is the hair of sheep. Weaving mills use it to make cloth."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Cloth
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:176 input:176 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid ""
"Cloth is needed to build several buildings. It is also consumed in the "
"sewing workshop, armor smithy and shipyard."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Straw
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:186 input:186 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid ""
"Straw is a by-product of wheat production. You need it for breeding animals."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Wheat Sheaf
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:194 input:194 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid ""
"Wheat sheaves are harvested by farmers who sent them to threshing floors to "
"gain wheat and straw."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Water, part 1
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:203 input:203 standard
msgctxt "ware"
msgid "Water is the essence of life!"
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Water, part 2
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:205 input:205 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid ""
"Water is used in multiple buildings. You need it for production of bricks, "
"for preparation of bread, elixirs and potions and for breeding animals."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Wheat, part 1
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:218 input:218 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid "Wheat is essential for survival."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Wheat, part 2
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:220 input:220 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid ""
"Wheat is produced by threshing floors and turned into flour by mills. Sheep "
"farms and cattle farms also need to be supplied with wheat."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Flour
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:231 input:231 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid ""
"Flour is produced by the miller out of wheat and it is needed in the bakery "
"to produce the tasty bread."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Fruit, part 1
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:241 input:241 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid ""
"Fruit is picked by gardeners in the orchard and used as a substitute of "
"vegetable by meal preparation."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Fruit, part 2
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:243 input:243 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid "Druids do also pick some secret fruit ingredients when poaching elixir."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Vegetable
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:254 input:254 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid ""
"Vegetable is used by meal preparation. If there is no vegetable in the "
"kitchen, fruit can be used instead."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Herbs, part 1
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:265 input:265 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid "Herbs are irreplaceable by preparation of elixir and potion."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Herbs, part 2
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:267 input:267 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid ""
"You need this two types of drinks in deep mines and for warrior training."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Fish
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:277 input:277 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid ""
"Fresh fish is smoked in the smokery and added into meals for your warriors "
"and miners."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Meat
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:288 input:288 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid ""
"Fresh meat is smoked in the smokery and added into meals for your warriors "
"and miners."
msgstr ""

