msgid "Can be replaced by milk."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Bread
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:324 input:324 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid ""
"Bread is used in kitchens to prepare rations and meals. Bread is also "
"consumed at the training sites (druid’s gatherings)."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Milk
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:333 input:333 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid ""
"Milk is used to prepare rations and meals. If there is no milk available, "
"cook can use smoked fish or smoked meat instead."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Ration, part 1
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:346 input:346 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid "A small bite to keep miners strong and working."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Ration, part 2
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:348 input:348 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid "The scout also consumes rations on his scouting trips."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Meal, part 1
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:359 input:359 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid ""
"A proper meal is made in the kitchen out of bread and either milk or smoked "
"fish or smoked meat and it also has to contain fruit or vegetable. It "
"satisfies the needs of miners in advanced mines."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Meal, part 2
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:361 input:361 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid "Meal is also consumed at the training sites (arenas, training camps)."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Coal, part 1
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:372 input:372 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid ""
"While smelting metals, the fires of the Gallic furnaces are fed with coal."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Coal, part 2
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:374 input:374 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid "It is mined in coal mines or produced out of logs by a charcoal kiln."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Copper Ore, part 1
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:385 input:385 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid "Copper ore can be smelted into copper in a furnace."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Copper Ore, part 2
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:387 input:387 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid "By adding some tin ore you can obtain bronze."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Help text for a Gallic ware: Copper, part 1
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:398 input:398 standard
msgctxt "gauls_ware"
msgid "Copper is a rare building material."
msgstr ""

