"The forester plants one tree between %1$s and %2$s, depending on how far he "
"has to walk."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose help text for a Gallic production site: Clay Pit
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:1494 input:1494 standard
msgctxt "gauls_building"
msgid ""
"Digs up mud from the ground and uses water to turn it into clay. Clay is "
"used to make bricks."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance help text for a Gallic production site: Clay Pit, part 1
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:1497 input:1497 standard
msgctxt "gauls_building"
msgid ""
"This building can produce one clay between %1$s and %2$s, depending on how "
"far the clay digger has to walk."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose help text for a Gallic production site: Stonecutter’s Hut
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:1507 input:1507 standard
msgctxt "gauls_building"
msgid "Cuts blocks of stone out of rocks in the vicinity."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note help text for a Gallic production site: Stonecutter’s Hut
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:1509 input:1509 standard
msgctxt "gauls_building"
msgid "The stonecutter needs rocks to cut within the work area."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance help text for a Gallic production site: Stonecutter’s Hut, part 1
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:1512 input:1512 standard
msgctxt "gauls_building"
msgid ""
"The stonecutter can produce one block of granite between %1$s and %2$s on "
"average, depending on how far he has to walk."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose help text for a Gallic production site: Well
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:1522 input:1522 standard
msgctxt "gauls_building"
msgid "Draws water out of the deep."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance help text for a Gallic production site: Well, part 1
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:1525 input:1525 standard
#, lua-format
msgctxt "gauls_building"
msgid "The carrier needs %s to get one bucket full of water."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance help text for a Gallic production site: Well, part 2
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:1527 input:1527 standard
#, lua-format
msgctxt "gauls_building"
msgid "If the water resource is depleted, the carrier needs %s on average."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose help text for a Gallic production site: Fisher's Hut
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:1535 input:1535 standard
msgctxt "gauls_building"
msgid "Fishes on the coast near the fisher’s house."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note help text for a Gallic production site: Fisher's Hut, Part 1
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:1538 input:1538 standard
msgctxt "gauls_building"
msgid "The fisher’s hut needs water full of fish within the work area."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note help text for a Gallic production site: Fisher's Hut, Part 2
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:1540 input:1540 standard
msgctxt "gauls_building"
msgid "Roads and trees along the shoreline block fishing."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance help text for a Gallic production site: Fisher's Hut, part 1
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:1544 input:1544 standard
msgctxt "gauls_building"
msgid ""
"This building can produce one fish between %1$s and %2$s, depending on how "
"far the fisher has to walk."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose help text for a Gallic production site: Hunter’s Hut
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:1554 input:1554 standard
msgctxt "building"
msgid "Hunts animals to produce meat."
msgstr ""

