#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:1618 input:1618 standard
msgctxt "gauls_building"
msgid ""
"The farmer can produce one bundle of reed between %1$s and %2$s on average, "
"depending on how far he has to walk."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose help text for a Gallic production site: Furnace
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:1628 input:1628 standard
msgctxt "gauls_building"
msgid "Smelts ore into iron, copper, bronze and gold."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance help text for a Gallic production site: Furnace
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:1630 input:1630 standard
msgctxt "gauls_building"
msgid ""
"If this building is fully supplied and there is a demand for all metals, "
"production of 6 iron ingots, 2 copper ingots, 3 bronze bars and 2 gold bars "
"takes %1$s. If only one kind of metal is needed, it takes %2$s to produce "
"one iron or copper ingot or %3$s to produce one bronze or gold bar."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose help text for a Gallic production site: Garden
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:1637 input:1637 standard
msgctxt "gauls_building"
msgid "Grows herbs and vegetable."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance help text for a Gallic production site: Garden, the gardener is a female
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:1640 input:1640 standard
msgctxt "gauls_building"
msgid ""
"If all products are needed by the economy, the gardener resp. experienced "
"gardener need %1$s resp. %2$s on average to produce two baskets of vegetable "
"and two bundles of herbs. If only one product is needed by the economy, the "
"gardener resp. experienced gardener need %3$s resp. %4$s on average to "
"produce one baskets of vegetable or one bundle of herbs."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose help text for a Gallic production site: Orchard
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:1648 input:1648 standard
msgctxt "gauls_building"
msgid "Plants fruit trees and harvests fruit."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note help text for a Gallic production site: Orchard
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:1650 input:1650 standard
msgctxt "gauls_building"
msgid ""
"According to the climate, two different fruit trees are planted – apple tree "
"and cherry tree. Per two fruit trees, one juniper – which has a form of a "
"bush – is planted."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance help text for a Gallic production site: Orchard, part 1, the gardener is a female
#: addons/gauls.wad/tribes/gauls_tribe/units.lua:1653 input:1653 standard
msgctxt "gauls_building"
msgid ""
"When the orchard has already multiple trees, the gardener can produce one "
"basket of fruit between %1$s and %2$s, depending on how far she has to walk."
msgstr ""

